room_title: Escape room "The Edge of the Enchanted Forest" by Trapped! Escape Room in Cleveland
room_description:
You’re on a tour of a historical home and the guide stops you all for a bathroom break. Your little group sneaks off to try and see some of the house that isn’t open to visitors, and you find yourselves in a tiny cupboard that leads you into a magical land.
Once you enter, Diyeardra the woodland fairy warns you that the Destroyers are coming. Your only escape is by proving your worthiness to the Tree of Travelers. Will you be worthy enough to pass the tests and escape without being destroyed?
